sequenceDiagram
    participant MultipleAgents
    participant AnalyticalEngines
    participant DecisionFusionEngine
    participant SupervisorAI
    participant HumanApproval

    MultipleAgents->>DecisionFusionEngine: Submit Outputs (Scores, Confidence)
    AnalyticalEngines->>DecisionFusionEngine: Submit Outputs (Insights, Recommendations)

    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Normalize Scores & Confidence
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Evaluate Evidence Quality
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Detect Contradictions
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Apply Configurable Weights
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Consider Risk & Uncertainty
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Produce Unified Decision
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Generate Alternative Scenarios
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Generate Confidence Intervals
    DecisionFusionEngine->>DecisionFusionEngine: Explain Decision Rationale

    alt High-Risk Action
        DecisionFusionEngine->>HumanApproval: Request Approval (Decision, Explanation, Evidence)
        HumanApproval-->>DecisionFusionEngine: Approval/Rejection
    end

    DecisionFusionEngine-->>SupervisorAI: Unified Decision (with Explanation, Evidence)
    SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Record Decision & Audit Trail
